{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund fully paid student paramedics placement hours",
        "additional_details": "Many students have to travel to their placement and have to fund their own education. We think paying student paramedics for placement hours would give them more recognition and support for their hard work.",
        "background": "Student paramedics work really hard within the ambulance service and they don\u2019t get the recognition that they should. They don\u2019t get paid for their placement hours, although they are also experiencing a cost of living crisis with inflation.",
